Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:45.94,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(246,0,246,130)\fs18\1a&H45&\4a&H2D&\4c&H0F0F0F&\shad1}临近海边  宁静的露天浴场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里还没去过天然的温泉吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我只在电视节目里看过介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会让身心都暖烘烘的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在下次放假的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真期待～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那蓝华也能去啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不能去我也要去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.22,0:09:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 那就大家一起去温泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去温泉要带什么好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈的话 不用你带也会一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和艾莉西亚前辈一起去温泉～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.11,0:09:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某人陷入妄想状态中了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！赶紧结束练习
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟艾莉西亚前辈一起去温泉啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邮递员先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的工作结束了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝吗？虽然可能有点不好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小妹妹的雪虫打扮得真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:09:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就要去体验第一次的温泉之旅了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬天要是水道的水也像温泉一样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老伯伯 烟囱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各家各户都开始用壁炉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬天的黄昏让人想家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 总觉得是个温暖的景象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暖洋洋的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里也来织织看吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能办得到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 灯里的话一定能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会努力织出跟艾莉西亚前辈配对的东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也给亚利亚社长织一套围巾和帽子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 首先棒针要这么拿…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后像这样把毛线用食指勾住…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不好意思 结果都是让蓝华去预约的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…我刚好知道一个很棒的温泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.84,0:12:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好期待哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经能看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(260,210)\fs34\frz6\c&HE0C8AA&\b1}土产
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请慢慢享受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.59,0:12:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这房间好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和期待的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 我们准备准备去泡温泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:12:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是灯里的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把脱下来的衣服放在里面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我第一次跟不认识的人一起泡大浴池…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 蓝华 我先进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我 等等我 等等我 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磨磨蹭蹭笨手笨脚 禁止…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路很滑 要注意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.61,0:13:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是温泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 很特别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:14:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实这里原来只是一个古旧的大宅子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有这座宅邸的是一对很有情调的老夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说他们发现温泉以后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆就把宅邸的一部分建成浴池了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建筑物本身虽然年久失修
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这也别有一番风味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像传说故事中的精灵之家一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温泉还延伸到更深处…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 来这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.83,0:14:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温泉水好舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:15:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗完澡果然还是要喝咖啡牛奶啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 很精通嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是正确的喝法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通体舒畅啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 舒服地泡完澡之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是令人期待的晚餐时间～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝佳的美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有冻死人的特训 暖洋洋的又悠闲…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼前不再是大嗓门的前辈 而是艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,极乐啊极乐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华 表情太陶醉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级像换了个人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗？我这样很幸福 所以别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为太舒服了 不小心就睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是这种时间了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时的这时候 工作已经告一段落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在准备晚餐了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实在这样的假日里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这个单手套领航员才该拼命练习才对的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像做了不该做的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样行吗？这么悠闲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让你这么悠闲也是温泉的魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了度过寒冷漫长的冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是需要喘口气的时间哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 虽然我不习惯冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有可爱的雪虫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有令人想家的夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有暖炉的话 好像也能变得喜欢冬天了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.36,0:16:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还泡了温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温泉 一定是AQUA的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送给我们的温暖的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要再去泡一次温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为人们说「温泉要泡三次」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我们也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈 没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边有一个秘密场地哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好黑…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级心惊肉跳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈…还没到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.15,0:17:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.43,0:18:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒 和大海连在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.54,0:18:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈 难道你来过这温泉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 但是不好意思说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你太见外了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海和温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 灯里 没规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是但是 这么宽广却不游泳很浪费啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这倒也是 好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 觉悟吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然冬天的空气很清新 星星看得很清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像又想睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.24,0:19:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桃子汽水 是这里的名产哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.19,0:19:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜甜的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好像作梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好悠闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饱喝足了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.87,0:19:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟您一起的客人已经到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晃前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没赶上晚餐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我请她们来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.65,0:20:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气氛不太热烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要通宵好好享受哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通宵？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从极乐…堕入了地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一套！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿咻！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再…出一身汗…才去温泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华接下来是艾莉西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要和你决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 我不想打了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.03,0:20:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪虫…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们为了过冬 要回到水曲柳上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？要道别了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 AQUA的雪虫非常长寿的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.06,0:21:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 到了明年的冬天一定还能见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.80,0:21:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.37,0:22:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.44,0:22:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在新威尼斯有个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.04,0:22:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「雪虫踏上旅程的时候就会下起初雪」的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.61,0:22:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪会那么冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.45,0:22:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.19,0:22:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.89,0:22:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 AQUA的冬天确实很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.83,0:22:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也有很多美好的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以后每年都会期待着冬天的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和雪虫也会再见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.97,0:22:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想来看看冬天的新威尼斯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.39,0:24:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们总有一天会成为独当一面的领航员的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.03,0:24:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要成为一个独立的正式领航员
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.33,0:24:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话…就…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.20,0:24:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.00,0:24:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些 橘色的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.27,0:24:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们一起度过美好的时光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:55.16,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}風が凪いて 振り返れば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:02:04.44,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}夕映えに 照らされ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:14.11,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}心までも 染まってゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.85,0:02:25.16,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}見上げれば 響きだす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:33.13,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}星たちの歌が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:43.28,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}さあ 漕ぎ出そう 遥か未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:52.32,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}水面に 夢 広がる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:03:06.87,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ねえ 見つけよう まだ知らない 宝物を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:13.14,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}あなたと一緒に 探そう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:17.34,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ウンディーネ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:55.16,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}轻风吹拂着 蓦然回首
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:02:04.44,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}映照在夕阳下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:14.11,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}让心中 染上温暖的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.85,0:02:25.16,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}抬头仰望 空中传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:33.13,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}是星星们的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:43.28,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}来 让我们出发 向着遥远的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:52.32,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}梦想 顺着水面 铺开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:03:06.87,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}快 让我们去寻找 那未被人知的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:13.14,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}跟你一起踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:17.34,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}水之精灵
