Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.19,0:23:00.66,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}不断变化的季节中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.13,0:23:08.67,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}寻觅到 那不变的想念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.00,0:23:12.97,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}听 那幸福的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.27,0:23:19.61,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}像这样 一直 满溢于心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.64,0:23:28.19,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}所有的梦想 都将实现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.52,0:23:31.46,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我们 总会越过彩虹
